snippet.title: Healthy Hero: Tower Defense (Prototype)
snippet.description:
Healthy Hero is a Tower Defense game where the player protects the hero from attacking junk food. You need to build and improve defense towers to stop the enemies. Levels get harder with new types of junk food and waves, but you can get items and improve towers. Be a real Healthy Hero and defeat the junk food!

Donate: https://www.donationalerts.com/r/benzej1
